CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,FSinn Fein is calling for the return of
OL,7,F50:50 recruitment in the PSNI after
OL,8,Ffigures released last week showed the
OL,9,Flowest number of Catholic applicants
OL,10,Fto join the service in a decade.
OL,12,FLast week it was confirmed that
OL,13,Ffollowing the latest PSNI recruitment
OL,14,Fcampaign, 4,105 people had applied.
OL,16,FPSNI data showed that 65.6% who
OL,17,Fapplied were from a Protestant
OL,18,Fbackground, 26.7% were Catholic, and
OL,19,F7.7% were undetermined.
OL,26,@nD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,FIt is the lowest percentage of
OL,7,Fapplicants from the Catholic community
OL,8,Fsince 2013, according to PSNI figures.
OL,10,FSinn Fein representatives met with the
OL,11,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher and other
OL,12,Fsenior officers at Stormont on Monday
OL,13,Fafternoon, as part of regular
OL,14,Fdiscussions.
OL,16,FAhead of the meeting, Policing Board
OL,17,Fmember and MLA Deirdre Hargey said her
OL,18,Fparty planned to raise the low
OL,19,Frecruitment figures with the Chief
OL,20,FConstable.
OL,26,@rD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,F50:50 recruitment was introduced
OL,7,Fbetween 2001 to 2011 to ensure that
OL,8,Ffor every Protestant recruit to the
OL,9,Fnewly formed PSNI, an applicant from a
OL,10,FCatholic background would also be
OL,11,Frecruited.
OL,13,FMs Hargey said: "I think removing it
OL,14,F(50:50 recruitment) in the first place
OL,15,Fwas a retrograde step back and I think
OL,16,Frecent figures show the impact that
OL,17,Fhas had.
OL,26,@uD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,F"So I think if something has worked
OL,7,Fand we saw that it worked between 2001
OL,8,Fand 2011 where numbers at that time
OL,9,Fwere 8% and they increased to over 30%.
OL,11,F"So it can be done and it's shown it
OL,12,Fcan be done and I think we need to
OL,13,Flook at what has worked well in the
OL,14,Fpast."
OL,16,FLast week, SDLP Policing Board member
OL,17,FColin McGrath MLA said the number of
OL,18,FCatholic applicants should signal
OL,19,Falarm bells.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,F"Unfortunately this trajectory has
OL,7,Fbeen clear for some time and these
OL,8,Ffigures are in no way surprising.
OL,9,FUnless we see drastic changes things
OL,10,Fwill only get worse, with Policing
OL,11,FBoard projections putting the number
OL,12,Fof officers from a Catholic background
OL,13,Fat just 23% in ten years' time.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,F"The reasons for the decline are
OL,7,Fcomplex and there are no easy answers.
OL,8,FThe threat from dissidents still looms
OL,9,Fin the background, the handling of
OL,10,Flegacy cases and a number of high-
OL,11,Fprofile mistakes, including the data
OL,12,Fbreach, would give many pause when
OL,13,Fconsidering a career in policing. I
OL,14,Fwelcome and appreciate the efforts of
OL,15,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher to
OL,16,Faddress these issues.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,F"When it comes to policing the SDLP
OL,7,Fhas never been found wanting, we have
OL,8,Fsupported the police and encouraged
OL,9,Fpeople to apply, even when it hasn't
OL,10,Falways been easy. Last year SDLP
OL,11,FLeader Claire Hanna called for an
OL,12,Findependent review of policing and the
OL,13,Frule of law institutions to stop this
OL,14,Fslide backwards. This must be taken
OL,15,Fseriously by the PSNI, the Executive
OL,16,Fand particularly the Justice Minister,
OL,17,Falongside the UK and Irish Governments.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,F"Without a major intervention this
OL,7,Fsituation will only get worse in the
OL,8,Fyears ahead with serious consequences
OL,9,Ffor confidence in policing and society
OL,10,Fas a whole."
OL,12,FDUP MLA Trevor Clarke, who serves as
OL,13,Fhis party's lead on the Policing
OL,14,FBoard, said calls to bring back 50:50
OL,15,Frecruitment are a 'lazy substitute for
OL,16,Fleadership' from the SDLP and Sinn
OL,17,FFein: "It is built on discrimination
OL,18,Fand would undermine merit at the very
OL,19,Fmoment we need the best people in
OL,20,Fpolicing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1771883656
OL,3,CCalls for return of 50:50 PSNI
OL,4,Crecruitment
OL,6,F"Those attacking the culture of the
OL,7,FPSNI and its history are often the
OL,8,Fsame voices who have spent years
OL,9,Fdiscouraging people from their own
OL,10,Fcommunities from joining.
OL,12,F"If there is a genuine desire for a
OL,13,Frepresentative police service, that
OL,14,Fstarts with encouragement and
OL,15,Fleadership - particularly in
OL,16,Fnationalism and republicanism - not
OL,17,Fpoliticisation or the dilution of
OL,18,Fstandards."
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@KO]
